qrList.label: 取消隐藏10层
qrList.message:
/let key=unhide_amount 10|

/let key=unhide_id_end 0|
/times guard=off {{lastMessageId}} {:
	/let key=reverse_id {:/sub {{lastMessageId}} {{timesIndex}}|:}()|
	/let key=FindMsg {:/messages names=on {{var::reverse_id}}|:}()|
    /if left=FindMsg right="{{noop}}" {:
    	/var key=unhide_id_end {{var::reverse_id}}|
    	/break|
    :}|
:}|
/breakpoint |
/if left={{var::unhide_id_end}} right=0 {:
	/var key=unhide_id_end {:/add {{pipe}} 1|:}()|
:}|
/let key=unhide_id_start {{var::unhide_id_end}}||

/if left={{var::unhide_id_end}} right={{var::unhide_amount}} rule=lt else={:
	/var key=unhide_id_start {:/sub {{var::unhide_id_end}} {{var::unhide_amount}}|:}()|
:} {:
	/var key=unhide_id_start 0|
:}|
/breakpoint |

/unhide {{var::unhide_id_start}}-{{var::unhide_id_end}}|
